# The example talks to the emulator through the standard BigQuery client.
# ``bqemulator`` itself is provided by the repo's editable install
# (``pip install -e ".[dev,all]"``) in CI, so it is not pinned here.
#
# google-cloud-bigquery 3.20 is CVE-clean per OSV; the cap stays at <4.0
# (3.x is the current major). Matches the floor used by the other Python
# examples to avoid forcing user upgrades.
google-cloud-bigquery>=3.20,<4.0
